        "paragraph_index": 1,
        "text": "### Reported Constants\n\nThe 2005 study by Demirel et al. is linked to **four VLM entries** in SRD-46, all measured at **37 В°C** and **I = 0.15 M**. The constants they reported cover three ZnВІвЃєвЂ“L-histidine species:\n\n| VLM ID | Equilibrium | Species | Type | Value | T (В°C) | I (M) |\n|--------|-------------|---------|------|-------|---------|-------|\n| vlm_98900 | ZnВІвЃє + LвЃ» в‡Њ ZnLвЃє | ZnL | log K | **6.35** | 37 | 0.15 |\n| vlm_98909 | ZnВІвЃє + 2 LвЃ» в‡Њ ZnLв‚‚ | ZnLв‚‚ | log ОІв‚‚ | **11.67** | 37 | 0.15 |\n| vlm_98920 | ZnL + HвЃє в‡Њ ZnHL | ZnHL (protonated) | log K | **4.61** | 37 | 0.15 |\n| vlm_98926 | ZnLв‚‚ + HвЃє в‡Њ ZnHLв‚‚ | ZnHLв‚‚ (protonated) | log K | **5.50** | 37 | 0.15 |",
